description:
A simple rod carved from wood. Designed as a starter
weapon, it leaves much to be desired.
name: Wooden Staff

description:
Imbued with rather weak magic. Sadly, this broom
cannot be flown.
name: Magic Broomstick

description:
<WordWrap>
A sweet-tasting magic staff made for kids. Although it's delectable, it's not edible.
name: Candy Cane

description:
A rod to maximize a user's power potential.
The ideal implement for a Luna's long journey.
name: Power Staff

description:
A bell infused with magic.
Made of glass reinforced with sorcery.
name: Diamond Chime

description:
A rod housing an earth spirit who is said to render
aid and comfort in times of trouble.
name: Earth Staff

description:
<WordWrap>
A staff crafted using treasured techniques handed down through generations of artisans.
name: Treasured Staff

description:
A rod carved from ice that never melts. Its rough
surface helps the holder keep a grip.
name: Ice Staff

description:
A hot rod that feels like fire in your hand.
Use it to make a cold bath nice and warm.
name: Fire Staff

description:
Crafted by an elderly blacksmith hobbyist.
It's as strong as any professional forging.
name: Old Man's Staff

description:
Staff imbued with the power of thunder.
A replica of one carried by a mythic god-beast.
name: Thunder Staff

description:
A staff infused with magic by a famous mage.
Holding it is enough to instill confidence.
name: Magic Wand

description:
A bell carved with ancient incantations to enhance
the power of magic.
name: Rune Bell

description:
This bell hangs from the belt of the grim reaper.
It rings when he harvests a soul.
name: Reaper's Bell

description:
A rod blessed by an angel. Its heavenly connection
gives it amazing power.
name: Angel's Staff

description:
A rod to shine hope in the dark. Let it fall and it
will point the way.
name: Light Staff

description:
They say that this bell's chimes bring luck.
The more you ring it, the better things get.
name: Continuity Bell

description:
A chic stick with a striped pattern. It doesn't just
look good- it's practical, too.
name: Striped Rod

description:
A rod made from a sacred tree over a thousand years
old. Has a rustic feel of natural wood.
name: Yew Staff

description:
A bell made sacred in a ceremony.
It is the twin of Susanne's Bell.
name: Marianne's Bell

description:
A bell made sacred in a ceremony.
It is the twin of Marianne's Bell.
name: Susanne's Bell

description:
A sorcerer's staff that summons a storm of spells.
So full of magic it's hot to the touch.
name: Hayate Staff

description:
A staff made from the special metal mythril. Useful
and VERY fashionable.
name: Mythril Rod

description:
A staff of miracles. Often found in the hands of
religious pilgrims and ascetics.
name: Shugen Stave

description:
It looks at tasty as a strawberry. Just one glance
can satisfy sugary cravings.
name: Strawberry Broom

description:
A rod dyed completely black. It redirects
the power of darkness, using it to attack enemies
name: Dark Staff

description:
Broom sweeps away fogs of darkness. Leave under
the eaves at night for a cloudless dawn.
name: Cloudsweeper Broom

description:
A rod made from the remnants of fallen stars. It
twinkles at night, longing for the sky.
name: Stardust Staff

description:
The rod held by the god of death. It was once
considered a very trendy item among the dead.
name: Judgement Staff

description:
A rod only the wisest may wield. Those who are
unqualified find it too powerful to handle.
name: Sage's Staff

description:
A rod made by cat lovers for cat lovers. Don't swing
it too wildly, or it'll make you dizzy.
name: Kitty Staff

description: A golden staff that burns everything in its path.
name: Burnout Broom

description: All Yuke ladies have owned at least one.
name: Fine Broom

description:
A bell that sounds a holy jingle on a holy day.
Heard only once a year.
name: Jingle Bell

description: Named for a goddess of the moon.
name: Ariane Rod

description:
A blade made from copper materials. Not very powerful.
Used primarily for practice.
name: Bronze Sword

description: A sword made from iron. A standard weapon.
name: Iron Sword

description:
A sword forged from steel.
Essential equipment for risk-taking adventurers.
name: Bastard Sword

description:
A sword made of lightweight materials.
Won't tire you out, even in a long fight.
name: Feather Saber

description:
<WordWrap>
A sword designed for total victory over foes. The best defense is a good offense!
name: Defender

description:
<WordWrap>
A sword forged using techniques handed down through generations of blacksmiths.
name: Treasured Blade

description:
A sword with a very chilly blade that never melts,
even in the hottest environments.
name: Ice Brand

description:
<WordWrap>
A sword enveloped in fire. The flames never go out, no matter how violently it is swung. \c[14]Deals double damage on undead and nature enemies.
name: Flametongue

description:
This sword was wielded by heroes.
It symbolizes victory in battle.
name: Hero's Sword

description:
<WordWrap>
Crafted by an elderly blacksmith hobbyist. It's as strong as any professional forging.
name: Old Man's Sword

description:
<WordWrap>
A sword that cuts through anything. An ancient heirloom from a distant country. \c[1]Has 20% chance to deal 3x critical damage.
name: Zantetsu

description:
Great sword made for heavy knights.
Really too heavy to be used much.
name: Claymore

description:
Blade forged using ancient methods.
It is the match of any modern blade.
name: Primeval Sword

description:
Weapon borne by the servant of a renowned hero.
Evokes a desire to serve.
name: Maid Blade

description:
A sword shimmering with a divine glow.
Said to dispel darkness and shine light on truth.
name: Light Blade

description:
Sword wielded by a king of legend. Reserved for those
who choose the way of the knight.
name: Calibum

description:
A blade for the truly courageous.
The cowardly find its weight too heavy to bear.
name: Brave Sword

description:
A solid, multi-edged sword.
Quite cumbersome, but can deliver tremendous blows.
name: Colossum Blade

description:
A sword that has vanquished evil all over the world.
Made to thwart all wickedness.
name: Evil Slayer

description:
A sword made from the special metal mythril.
Mythril is easy to maintain.
name: Mythril Sword

description:
A sword forged with the utmost care.
It is a masterpiece created for connoisseurs.
name: Kotetsu

description:
A blade noted in the folklore of Rebena Te Ra.
Its outdated appearance belies great power.
name: Legendary Sword

description:
A blade that gleams with a special light.
Platinum is reserved only for the very best.
name: Platinum Edge

description:
A sword stained the color of night. It is said that
the weapon can cut through light itself.
name: Dark Blade

description:
A famous sword that brought countless victories
to the conquerors who carried it.
name: Excalibur

description:
Seven sacred stones that twinkle like stars are
embedded in this holy sword.
name: Septentrio Blade

description:
<WordWrap>
A sword carried by one who saved the world. Grants 25% critical strike chance.
name: Ultima Weapon

description: A wicked sword of treachery and betrayal.
name: Laevateinn

description:
A precious and extremely rare sword.
Once seen in a great tower in another world.
name: Seven-Prong Sword

description:
A sword made in a foreign land.
Used to instill the spirit of bushido.
name: Bamboo Sword

description: The fantastical sword said to herald the world's end.
name: Ragnarok Sword

description:
A one-hit, one-kill blade used in sword fights
to the death.
name: Bushido Sword

description:
A single-edged dagger made of bronze. It was designed
to be small and easy to carry
name: Bronze Knife

description:
A double-edged dagger designed to be more apt for
battle.
name: Dagger

description:
This dagger is made from a rare and precious metal,
yet still has a modest look.
name: Mythril Knife

description:
A small knife that is usually used by thieves as a
secondary weapon.
name: Second Knife

description:
An ordinary-looking dagger that has the ability to put
foes to sleep.
name: Sleep Dagger

description:
This dagger gifts its wielder with a catlike evasion
that really annoys enemies.
name: Main Gauche

description: A short blade that boosts its wielder's HP.
name: Survival Edges

description:
Cut their victims once and let the poison take its
course. No fuss, just one small graze and it's done.
name: Toxic Dagger

description:
This blade deprives those it cuts of speech,
preventing spells. Enjoy the silence.
name: Mage Masher

description:
A relatively high-quality dagger that shines in a
radiant white hue.
name: Platinum Dagger

description:
A short sword from a faraway world which boasts
high attack power against aquatic monsters.
name: Orichalcum

description:
A unique comb-like short sword. As its name would
suggest, it was made to break certain weapons (-Atk).
name: Swordbreaker

description:
A smith imbued this dagger with the power of wind,
simply because he could.
name: Air Knife

description:
Rumor has it that this kitchen knife belonged to
a great chef.
name: Kitchen Knife

description:
Though normally criminal behavior, stealing from
monsters is indeed permissible.
name: Thief's Knife

description:
The dancer's soul within this dagger causes your body
to move of its own accord.
name: Dancing Dagger

description:
The name says it all. Killing monsters isn't
assassination, but who's counting?
name: Assassin's Dagger

description:
This red and black dagger is popular among
thieves and looks sweet at your hip.
name: Zwill Crossblade

description:
This blade presents a danger even to the wielder.
Keep out of the hands of cowards.
name: Valiant Knife
note:
Knife that grows in power as its wielder's
HP dwindles.

description:
A small and poisonous blade designed specially for
assassins. Its small size can be easily concealed.
name: Venomous Blade

description:
<WordWrap>
A simple bow hewn from wood. A starter weapon, it was made with the user safety in mind.
name: Wooden Bow

description:
<WordWrap>
A genuine archer's bow reinforced with iron. A powerful battle weapon.
name: Iron Bow

description:
<WordWrap>
A bow used by hunters to protect the forest. Very durable and popular with travelers.
name: Ranger's Bow

description:
A bow longer than most. Used by the yeomen of
a distant royal kingdom.
name: Long Bow

description:
<WordWrap>
A bow made using treasured techniques handed down through generations of bow makers.
name: Treasured Bow

description:
A bow as clear as ice. Arrows shot from it have
a very chilling effect.
name: Frost Bow

description:
<WordWrap>
A bow enveloped in perpetual fire. Able to shoot flaming arrows.
name: Flame Bow

description:
Bow of an archer who saved a forest in crisis.
Famed for its light and sturdy construction.
name: Hero's Bow

description:
Crafted by an elderly blacksmith hobbyist.
It's as strong as any professional forging.
name: Old Man's Bow

description:
A holy bow able to drive away demons.
The sound of the string alone makes them flee.
name: Exorcist Bow

description:
A bow powerful enough to raze buildings.
Its great weight demands an archer with muscle.
name: Ballista

description:
Fabled favorite of angelic archers.
Smitten foes are suppose to turn mad with love.
name: Angel's Bow

description:
A faintly shimmering bow imbued with magic.
An indestructible string gives it a long life.
name: Elfin Bow

description:
A bow modeled after fabled fantastical fowl creatures.
It has a distinctive... scent.
name: Chocobow

description:
A giant bow that fires a massive bolt.
Can even knock down castle walls.
name: Arbalest

description:
A bow that shines with sacred light.
Blessed by the gods of the hunt.
name: Artemis's Bow

description:
Named after a heavy weapon of another age.
The powerful recoil makes it difficult to use.
name: Leopold

description:
A legendary bow said to crush despair.
Arrows shot from it form streaks of light in the air.
name: Abyss Killer

description:
The bow of a god worshiped by hunters.
The arrows it fires always find their mark.
name: Ur's Bow

description:
A bow born of winds high in the sky.
Arrows shot from it fly like tornado missiles.
name: Aeolian Bow

description:
A bow made from the special metal mythril.
The string, too, is spun from molten metal.
name: Mythril Bow

description:
The bow with a sting in its tail.
Attacks the target like a swarm of wasps.
name: Wasp Sting

description:
Weapon of a famous foreign bowman.
It demands strength and an unclouded spirit.
name: Yoichi's Bow

description:
A bow used by one who stole from the rich to give to
the poor. A favorite among Selkies.
name: Loxley Bow

description:
A bow inspired by the rare red bird of mystery,
perhaps related to the phoenix?
name: Red Chocobow

description:
A bow dyed completely black.
Strike unseen at the enemy in the black of night.
name: Dark Bow

description:
A bow that delivers passion in an arrow. 
Sets the heart aflame!
name: Passion Bow

description:
Its arrows fly like swans.
In legends, a white swan gave birth to divine twins.
name: White Swan Bow

description:
A bow blessed by the gods of archers.
Its arrows fly straight to the foes heart.
name: Sagittarius' Bow

description:
This bow has saved the queen countless times.
It drives away monsters of darkness.
name: Save the Queen

description:
A bow that breaks the laws of Nature.
The random flight of the arrow is an illusion.
name: Deception Bow

description:
A bow made from the remains of the Fire Mountain Lava
Spider. Not for the squeamish.
name: Spider Bow

description:
A pretty little bow decorated with hearts.
Its arrows work better than any love potion!
name: Pretty Bow

description:
A bow containing the soul of a magic beast.
It has been born and reborn countless times.
name: Karma Bow

description: A lance forged of bronze. Often used in training.
name: Bronze Lance

description:
Standard-issue military pike.
Made for cost performance, not battle performance.
name: Soldier's Pike

description: A five-pronged pike. Made for thrusting attacks.
name: Partisan

description:
A spear forged of iron. 
A standard weapon, widely available.
name: Iron Lance

description:
A pike with a lantern on the end.
It can light your way in the dark.
name: Lantern Lance

description:
Issued to the mounted dragoons,
it symbolizes membership in that high-flying troop.
name: Dragoon Spear

description:
A lance forged using treasured techniques handed down
by generations of blacksmiths.
name: Treasured Pike

description:
A weapon born in an icy blizzard. 
Pleasantly cool to the touch.
name: Ice Lance

description:
A weapon born in the heart of flames.
Burns to a crisp all that it pierces.
name: Flame Lance

description:
Wielded by the mounted dragoons, 
it is famous among those who yearn for the sky.
name: High End

description:
Crafted by an elderly blacksmith hobbyist.
It's as strong as any professional forging.
name: Old Man's Lance

description:
A pike that strikes like lightning. 
It gives a little jolt when you touch it.
name: Thunder Pike

description: Peerless weapon wielded by a legendary pikeman.
name: Mataza's Spear

description:
A spear carved with ancient incantations to honor
the souls of the dead.
name: Rune Spear

description:
Spear issued to royal guards.
It serves as a standard for knights of the kingdom.
name: Guard's Pike

description: A lance forged of bronze. Often used in training.
name: Bronze Lance

description:
A pike crafted by an old, obsolete method.
Contains the distilled wisdom of the ancients.
name: Primeval Pike

description:
The grim reaper's pike.
The lantern on the end draws souls to him like moths.
name: Reaper's Pike

description:
A lance that moves at the speed of sound, 
too fast for the eye to catch.
name: Sonic Lance

description:
A lance infused with holy power. 
Sacred light dispels darkness with every thrust.
name: Holy Lance

description:
The pike of a sky dragon. 
The ruler of the heavens is carved upon the shaft.
name: Sky Lance

description:
A lance treasured by Lilities.
It finds foes as if it had a mind of its own.
name: Brionac

description:
Used to hunt giant sea monsters. 
Can pierce even the thickest hides.
name: Harpoon

description:
A pike wielded by a Lilty hero.
Its power does honor the hero's name.
name: Hero's Pike

description:
Made for a Lilty warrior. It's a perfect match
for the warrior's superhuman strength.
name: Halbred

description:
This despotic weapon is difficult to wield even for
master spearman.
name: Tyrant's Spear

description:
A pike that strikes like a tornado. 
Hot winds howl when the point strikes home.
name: Tornado Pike

description:
A pike made from the special metal mythril. 
The sharp point can skewer any foe.
name: Mythril Pike

description:
A spear with a very hard tip that was made to
resemble the horn of a wild animal.
name: Gemsbock

description:
A pike wielded by a warrior of a foreign land.
Its tip can spear a dragonfly in flight.
name: Tonbogiri

description:
A lance of legend. It was wielded by a knight who
always stood by the hero's side.
name: Camelot Lance

description: A lance forged of bronze. Often used in training.
name: Weather Cock

description:
A lance dyed blacker than black.
Can pierce to depths where no light ever reaches.
name: Dark Lance

description:
The kind of pike all knights love.
Lends courage to those who wield it.
name: Cresta's Pike

description: A pike that cleanses impurity and exorcises all evil.
name: Purification Pike

description:
The tusk of a giant ocean-going beast. 
Resilient like a rope but harder than steel.
name: Whale Tusk

description:
A sacred weapon with a raven spearhead.
Used in the battle of the gods.
name: Gungnir

description:
A magic pike that has plucked countless lives.
When thrust, it splits into 30 barbs.
name: Gae Bolg

description:
It bears the name of a legendary unicorn,
and it is modeled on the horn of that beast.
name: Canhur

description: A lance infused with the power of the sky gods.
name: Lance of Longinus

description:
The oath to the red god grants courage
to he who bears his spear.
name: Crimson Oath

description: A weapon crafted to symbolize the majesty of the king.
name: Obelisk

description:
Made with the horn of the legendary beast...
but perhaps it was the nose of a Mu?
name: Unicorn Horn

description:
Wielded by the god of the sea,
this spear can summon storms.
name: Trident

description: A lance forged of bronze. Often used in training.
name: Dragon Tusk

description:
A harp embellished with silver. It can easily lose its
luster, rendering its effects weaker.
name: Silver Harp

description:
A mysterious harp that plays a wonderfully soothing
sound. Weaves a sleep-inducing melody.
name: Dream Harp

description:
A standing harp. The song of its strings resembles
that of the lamia.
name: Lamia's Harp

description:
Harp immersed in the power of the sun. Effective
against dragons and undead.
name: Apollo's Harp
